    "The table notes provide additional details on how time savings and usage frequencies are coded.",
    "Sample: The figure is based on all completed responses from the 2024 survey that can be linked to the registry data.",
    "The widespread adoption of AI chatbots-and the substantial gender gaps in usage-are well documented in the literature.",
    "37 We contribute to this evidence by documenting that employer initiatives for AI chatbot adoption are now common and play an important role in shaping overall adoption rates and demographic disparities in usage.",
    "38 The importance of employer policies in driving adoption aligns with Dillon et al. (2025), who show that firm effects are a key determinant of workers' uptake of a randomized offer for Microsoft Copilot."
